reviewText: This is one of the highest quality reggae videos that I have seen in years. The flow is on point,the music is good,and it can be enjoyed by dual sexes. Burst of energy DVD.Recommended to all.
If you are looking for dancehall videos, remixes and footage you can't find else where (elephant man live in the studio, dancheall queen candy dutty wine remix) then this is where its at..

All this is, is a series of videos that can be downloaded for much cheaper and in unedited versions.  Don't get this as it is likely not what you are looking for.  Not that I know what you are looking for, but if you are anything like me...you are looking for something that has honeys all over the place, dancin an doin they thang.  If that is the case...this DVD is not for you.  lol
If you're a fan of Dancehall Reggae, this DVD is a must have. The remixes are wicked and everything flows perfectly. wicked videos!
